RESEARCH ALERT - Logicon raised . - - Merrill Lynch analyst Byron Callan said he raised his near - term rating on Logicon Inc to accumulate from neutral and his long - term rating to buy from neutral . - - He cited the stock ' s valuation and the company ' s potential for future acquisitions . - - " They have had successful acquisitions in the past , very much so , and they have the cash position and balance sheet to do it again , " Callan said . 
